fields.fullDescription:
About this item
Ample Storage Capacity: With a generous capacity of 3.2 cubic feet, this mini fridge (measuring 18.5" by 19.4" by 33.3") provides ample space to store a variety of beverages, snacks, and fresh produce.
The standard mini fridge's separate freezer compartment allows you to store frozen goods, such as ice cream, frozen meals, and ice cubes, keeping them easily accessible alongside your refrigerated items.
The fridge's new modern and elegant stainless steel exterior not only adds a touch of sophistication to any space but also ensures durability and easy cleaning, complementing your decor.
Inside the fridge, you'll find adjustable glass shelves, door bins, and a crisper drawer, offering flexibility to customize the storage space according to your needs and preferences.
